because they consider bishops to be superior than knights. I see none of that
in this position and a great fight lies ahead.} 16. f4 Qd7 {Connecting the
rooks.} 17. h3 Ra7 {Removing the rook from the diagonal and protecting c7 just
in case.} 18. Qc6 Rd8 19. Qxd7 Rxd7 20. Be3 Ne7 21. g4 h5 22. Bf3 Nfd5 23. gxh5
Nf5 24. Kf1 Kh7 25. Rc4 Kh6 26. Ke2 Nf6 27. Rd1 Nxh5 28. d5 exd5 29. Rxd5 Rxd5
30. Bxd5 c5 31. Rc3 Rd7 32. Ba2 Nf6 33. Rd3 Nd4+ 34. Kf1 a4 35. Bb1 Kh5 36. Kg2
Nd5 37. Rd1 g6 38. Bd3 f5 39. Kg3 Nf6 40. Bxd4 Rxd4 41. Be2+ Kh6 42. Rxd4 cxd4
43. Bb5 Ne4+ 44. Kf3 Nc5 45. Bc6 Nd3 46. Bb5 Nc5 47. Bc6 Kg7 48. Bb5 Kf7 49.
